            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/nhd/selected-topics/simplification-for-business/the-altinn-portal.html?id=614072" title="">
                        The Altinn Portal
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Editorial article, Ministry of Trade and Industry, 10.09.2010]</p>
                <p>The Altinn portal is the Norwegian authorities’ joint solution for reporting and dialogue with business and industry. Altinn has not only made Norwegian business and industry more efficient, but also made an important contribution to the modernisation of the public sector.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
