                        ILO and IMF conference in Oslo to address ways of accelerating a job-rich crisis recovery
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of Finance, 18.08.2010]</p>
                <p>ILO and IMF announced a joint conference to be hosted by the Prime Minister of Norway, Jens Stoltenberg, on 13 September 2010, in Oslo, to explore new ways of forging a sustainable, job-rich recovery from the global economic crisis. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
